ass Sie sich den ganzen Tag frei und bequem bewegen können.&nbsp;</font></p><p><font color="#000000"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;Egal, ob Sie zu Hause unterwegs sind oder eine schnelle Wanderung machen, Sie werden das luftige Gefühl und die uneingeschränkte Bewegungsfreiheit dieser leichten isolierte Stiefel zu schätzen wissen.</font></p><p><font color="#000000"><br></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709026996333" class="gf_row gf_equal-height gf_row-gap-10" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709026996333" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;" data-row-gap="10px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1685516813895" data-id="1685516813895" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753919325" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753919325"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(104, 158, 5);">70% RABATT</span></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996336" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996336" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragr